  <div class="hero-wrap">
    <div class="hero-copy reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">Premium digital lab</div>
      <h1>We build <span class="gold">sharp digital products</span> that feel alive.</h1>
      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:26px">Websites, SaaS dashboards, server infrastructure, automations and idea-to-product execution — designed with depth, motion and performance.</p>
      <div class="btn-row"><a class="btn primary" href="#work">Explore our work</a><a class="btn" href="#market">Sell an idea</a></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-card reveal" id="hero3d">
      <div class="orbital">
        <div class="grid3d"></div>
        <div class="device main"><div class="metric">LIVE PRODUCT SYSTEM</div><div class="bar"></div><div class="screen-grid"><div class="mini"></div><div class="mini"></div><div class="mini"></div><div class="mini"></div><div class="mini"></div><div class="mini"></div></div></div>
        <div class="device side"><div class="metric">99.9% UPTIME</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line" style="width:70%"></div></div>
        <div class="device small"><div class="metric">API READY</div><div class="bar" style="height:8px"></div></div>
        <div class="float-badge">3D · WEB · CLOUD</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="ticker"><div class="track"><span><b>✦</b> Web Development</span><span><b>✦</b> Server Management</span><span><b>✦</b> UI/UX Design</span><span><b>✦</b> SaaS Products</span><span><b>✦</b> Idea Marketplace</span><span><b>✦</b> API Integrations</span><span><b>✦</b> Web Development</span><span><b>✦</b> Server Management</span><span><b>✦</b> UI/UX Design</span><span><b>✦</b> SaaS Products</span><span><b>✦</b> Idea Marketplace</span><span><b>✦</b> API Integrations</span></div></div>

<section class="section" id="services">
  <div class="reveal"><div class="eyebrow">What we do</div><h2>Not generic sections. <span class="gold">Real product capabilities.</span></h2><p class="lead" style="margin-top:18px">Every service is built around business impact: speed, security, clean UI and long-term maintainability.</p></div>
  <div class="services">
    <article class="service big tall reveal"><div class="icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 18v3"/></svg></div><h3>Immersive Websites</h3><p>Premium landing pages, portfolios and company sites with smooth scroll, 3D depth, animations and conversion-focused structure.</p></article>
    <article class="service reveal"><div class="icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"/></svg></div><h3>SaaS Dashboards</h3><p>Admin panels, analytics, CRM flows and operational web apps.</p></article>
    <article class="service reveal"><div class="icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2v20M4 7h16M6 17h12"/></svg></div><h3>Server Ops</h3><p>VPS setup, deployments, SSL, backups, monitoring and support.</p></article>
    <article class="service reveal"><div class="icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M8 12h8M12 8v8"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/></svg></div><h3>Integrations</h3><p>Payment gateways, APIs, CRMs, automations and webhooks.</p></article>
    <article class="service big reveal"><div class="icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3 7 7 1-5 5 1 7-6-4-6 4 1-7-5-5 7-1z"/></svg></div><h3>Idea Marketplace</h3><p>Founders can submit product ideas. We evaluate, buy, list, design or build them into launch-ready products.</p></article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="immersive-band" id="market">
  <div class="band-inner">
    <div class="reveal"><div class="eyebrow">Scroll story</div><h2>From raw idea to launchable product.</h2><p class="lead" style="margin-top:18px">We do not just "make pages." We help shape the offer, design the experience, build the system and support it after launch.</p><div class="btn-row"><a href="#contact" class="btn primary">Submit your idea</a></div></div>
