<section class="section" id="process">
  <div class="reveal"><div class="eyebrow">How we work</div><h2>From idea to launch, built like a product lab.</h2><p class="lead" style="margin-top:16px">A sharp workflow with clear decisions, visible progress, and a polished handover — not random development.</p></div>
  <div class="process-lab reveal">
    <div class="process-road">
      <div class="process-visual" aria-hidden="true">
        <!-- Multiple Orbit Rings -->
        <div class="process-orbit o-1"></div>
        <div class="process-orbit o-2"></div>
        <div class="process-orbit o-3"></div>
        
        <div class="process-core">
          <div class="core-inner">
            Plan<br>Build<br>Launch
          </div>
          <div class="core-glow"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Animated Floating Chips -->
        <div class="process-chip c-1"><b>01 Brief</b>Goals, users, scope</div>
        <div class="process-chip c-2"><b>02 Visual</b>Look, flow, screens</div>
        <div class="process-chip c-3"><b>03 Sprint</b>Code, review, refine</div>
        <div class="process-chip c-4"><b>04 Deploy</b>Domain, SSL, monitor</div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-list">
        <div class="step reveal"><div class="num">01</div><h3>Discover the real goal</h3><p>We convert your idea into clear pages, features, users, and success metrics.</p><div class="mini-meta"><span>Scope</span><span>Requirements</span><span>Direction</span></div></div>
        <div class="step reveal"><div class="num">02</div><h3>Design the premium experience</h3><p>We create a strong visual direction with clean sections, modern UI, and mobile-first layouts.</p><div class="mini-meta"><span>UI/UX</span><span>Brand feel</span><span>Prototype</span></div></div>
        <div class="step reveal"><div class="num">03</div><h3>Build with stable interactions</h3><p>We develop responsive code, interactive areas, modals, animations, and sections that feel smooth.</p><div class="mini-meta"><span>Frontend</span><span>Backend-ready</span><span>Performance</span></div></div>
        <div class="step reveal"><div class="num">04</div><h3>Launch and hand over</h3><p>We deploy, test, connect domain/SSL, and prepare the site so it is easy to maintain.</p><div class="mini-meta"><span>Deployment</span><span>SSL</span><span>Support</span></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="process-note"><span><b>Result:</b> a website that looks premium, explains your offer clearly, and gives visitors something to interact with.</span><a class="btn" href="#contact">Start a project →</a></div>
  </div>
</section>

